  <parts>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name>Woman</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“Why are they doing it to us?” asks a desperate-looking woman when you make a mistake of wandering too close to her. “Why won’t they leave us alone?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What are you talking about?”</text>
          <def_link>8127</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave her alone.</text>
          <def_link>8126</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8125</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name>Woman</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“The soldiers. They want to destroy this city but the Gods won’t let them, would they?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.gnz_npc_oldman_met = true;</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Don’t worry, my child, you’re safe. The Gods will strike down the wicked and reward the righteous.”</text>
          <def_link>8130</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I’ve yet to see the Gods lifting up a finger to help anyone. At best they’re indifferent.”</text>
          <def_link>8129</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8127</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name>Woman</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“They helped us during the War,” says the woman, scoffing at you. “They won’t abandon us now, you’ll see.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave her alone.</text>
          <def_link>8126</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8129</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“The Gods don’t seem to be in any hurry,” snaps an old man, joining the conversation. “We’ve been here almost a month and it’s only getting worse.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Careful, old man. This kind of talk will get you in trouble.”</text>
          <def_link>8131</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I take it you’ve lost your faith.”</text>
          <def_link>8134</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8130</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I speak the truth,” says the old man stubbornly. “I didn’t come here to live in this shack, waiting for the soldiers to breach the walls and slaughter everyone. If Meru could really talk to the Gods, they would have helped us already.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why won’t you leave?”</text>
          <def_link>8132</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why did you come here?”</text>
          <def_link>8133</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Do the zealots bother you?”</text>
          <def_link>8137</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8131</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“And where would we go, o wise one?” asks the old man mockingly. “We sold everything we had to come here. Now we have nothing to go back to.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why did you come here?”</text>
          <def_link>8133</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Do the zealots bother you?”</text>
          <def_link>8137</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8132</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“One of the preachers talked us into it. Said that the old world is ending and the Gods are finally returning to right the wrongs and ease our sufferings. So we sold everything and went to the Holy City. ‘Course I don’t need to tell you this isn’t how I imagined it.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I take it you’ve lost your faith.”</text>
          <def_link>8134</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8133</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“They bother everyone but so far they have bigger fish to fry.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I take it you’ve lost your faith.”</text>
          <def_link>8134</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8137</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“You might say that,” admits the old man, glancing around.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[persuasion][streetwise]“Did you expect to be rewarded for showing up? The Gods are testing you. They want to see if you’re worthy of their love and care. They sent us the siege, the hardships to separate the wheat from the chaff. Which are you, old man?”</text>
          <def_link>8135</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick>
            <string>(aod.persuasion + aod.streetwise) &gt;= 10</string>
          </checksOnClick>
          <linksOnClick>
            <int>8136</int>
          </linksOnClick>
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Blind faith is fool's gold. You're better off without it.”</text>
          <def_link>8139</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8134</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>[failure]“I’ve heard this bullshit a hundred times,” says the old man angrily, turning away.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave.</text>
          <def_link>8126</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8135</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>[success]“You really think the Gods will stop the Aurelians?” asks the old man with hope.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[persuasion][charisma]“I know so. Mark my words, the city won’t fall for the Gods themselves are watching over it.”</text>
          <def_link>8135</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick>
            <string>(aod.persuasion + aod.cha) &gt;= 14</string>
          </checksOnClick>
          <linksOnClick>
            <int>8138</int>
          </linksOnClick>
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[charisma]“The Gods work in mysterious ways. You must have faith, brother.”</text>
          <def_link>8135</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick>
            <string>aod.cha &gt;= 9</string>
          </checksOnClick>
          <linksOnClick>
            <int>8138</int>
          </linksOnClick>
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[streetwise][charisma]“The Aurelians haven’t attacked yet, have they? Ask yourself why.”</text>
          <def_link>8135</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick>
            <string>(aod.streetwise + aod.cha) &gt;= 14</string>
          </checksOnClick>
          <linksOnClick>
            <int>8138</int>
          </linksOnClick>
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8136</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>[success]“May the Gods watch over you,” says the old man, looking relieved if only for a moment.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>rwd_reputation(GNZ_OldMan_01);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave.</text>
          <def_link>8126</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8138</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“You've come all the way to tell me that?” scoffs the old man, turning away.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
